org.tagaprice.core.entities
Class Receipt

java.lang.Object
  org.tagaprice.core.entities.Receipt
All Implemented Interfaces:
java.io.Serializable
@Entity
public class Receipt
extends java.lang.Object
implements java.io.Serializable

Represents a single receipt.

Holds information about the creator (see Account), the date when this receipt was created, a reference to basic shop information of this receipt and all ReceiptEntrys of this receipt.

TODO This class should be immutable. control collections-access.

Constructor Detail

Receipt

public Receipt(java.lang.Long id,
               BasicShop basicShop,
               java.util.Date createdAt,
               Account creator,
               java.util.Set<ReceiptEntry> receiptEntries)
Initializes a new Receipt.

Parameters:
id - Id of this receipt. If this is null, this entity is regarded to be new to the database. If set, must be > 0.
basicShop - BasicShop where this Receipt is from. At least, the id must be set. This BasicShop won't get persisted when this object is persisted. It must be already persisted.
createdAt - Date this receipt was created at.
creator - Account who created this receipt.
receiptEntries - ReceiptEntrys to be persisted with this receipt.
